Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(main)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.10,0:01:33.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,富士山很大
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.35,0:01:37.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爬起来比想象中困难得多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.77,0:01:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和日向学姐正在全力冲顶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.94,0:01:47.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肩负小葵学姐和小枫学姐的心意 一步一步…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.25,0:01:55.31,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\bord2\pos(1044,230)}不干了!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.36,0:01:50.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.28,0:01:53.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.63,0:01:57.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头还疼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.67,0:02:01.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 比刚才好点了 但还很疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.09,0:02:06.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 马上就天亮了 要不要看日出
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.34,0:02:10.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得来一趟 稍微加把劲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.18,0:02:12.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.64,0:02:16.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外面很冷的 上身再穿一件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.03,0:02:23.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 还借来了妈妈的羽绒服
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.34,0:02:27.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好难受
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.32,0:02:29.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不想动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.38,0:02:35.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还差一点 还差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.83,0:02:39.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 那就是山顶的鸟居
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.09,0:02:42.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还差一点 还差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.23,0:02:57.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 日出！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.44,0:03:03.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在这边等着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.81,0:03:04.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.71,0:03:10.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就要破晓了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.65,0:03:16.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人都面朝同一个方向
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.15,0:03:19.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多么强烈的归属感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.93,0:03:40.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日出 Amazing! Oh my god!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.32,0:03:53.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不虚此行呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.30,0:03:54.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.37,0:04:02.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.48,0:04:08.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.63,0:04:12.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.29,0:04:15.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…我的身体这么不争气
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.49,0:04:18.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.54,0:04:20.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不甘心…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.24,0:04:28.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在山顶 小葵没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.81,0:04:30.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.20,0:04:32.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高原反应下山就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.71,0:04:35.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这就下山
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.77,0:04:37.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用着急
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.94,0:04:40.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得来一次 绕山顶一周如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.80,0:04:41.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山顶一周？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.60,0:04:44.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,围着火山口绕一周
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.04,0:04:47.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个半小时到两个小时左右就能绕一圈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.68,0:04:48.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妨试试看？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.14,0:04:51.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们先回五合目
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.01,0:04:53.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下来了电话联络
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.34,0:04:58.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话腿已经没劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.43,0:05:01.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向学姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.77,0:05:03.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:07.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可可娜酱 吃了便当绕山顶一圈吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.45,0:05:12.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便当好香
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.65,0:05:13.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猪肉汤也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.07,0:05:16.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,登山肚子饿得真快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.83,0:05:18.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,登山真费体力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.43,0:05:22.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前面路还长 要好好补充体力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.01,0:05:23.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.76,0:05:29.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好惊人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:32.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚还黑漆漆的什么都看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.38,0:05:36.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼前只有岩石 白云 和蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.84,0:05:39.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直像是在天空散步呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:40.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.33,0:05:42.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳好耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.70,0:05:45.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风凉凉的好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.21,0:05:51.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像仙人掌一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.87,0:06:09.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,写信？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.66,0:06:11.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想给小葵写一封
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.94,0:06:15.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少 想把现在的心情传达给她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.60,0:06:17.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 我也写！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.12,0:06:22.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.65,0:06:23.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还差一步
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.96,0:06:37.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头和腿一起疼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.79,0:06:40.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但必须往前走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.89,0:06:43.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢走 不要勉强
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.96,0:06:44.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.38,0:06:50.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 小枫学姐一点没有不耐烦 还陪着我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.81,0:06:53.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明害她没上山顶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.66,0:06:57.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终点远在天边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.23,0:07:01.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走啊走 就是到不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.37,0:07:03.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要走多远啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.51,0:07:08.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要走到哪天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.80,0:07:16.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小枫学姐 还有多远啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.51,0:07:21.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵 咱们稍微歇会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.61,0:07:28.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得 尽量不要去想什么时候到比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.50,0:07:32.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你越是想 就越是到不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.62,0:07:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走的时候把大脑放空 不知不觉之间就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:40.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.54,0:07:49.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 为什么明明这么难过 我却还在登山
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.12,0:07:53.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 我为什么来这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.84,0:08:00.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腿好重
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.61,0:08:04.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这是最后的攀登
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.73,0:08:17.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.42,0:08:24.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑峰 3776米！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:29.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日本最高峰！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.07,0:08:46.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万岁 万岁…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.73,0:08:47.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wonderful
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.94,0:08:50.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,富士山太棒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.56,0:08:51.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wonderful～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.94,0:08:55.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万岁 万岁…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.44,0:08:59.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万岁 万岁…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.28,0:09:14.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,征服富士山咯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.58,0:09:16.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万岁 Yeah～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.75,0:09:21.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了？ 辛苦辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.73,0:09:23.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 在休息呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.19,0:09:27.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离巴士发车还有时间 去买些纪念品如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.04,0:09:28.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.11,0:09:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊 下次来的时候搭我一程吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.09,0:09:37.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 说好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.10,0:09:39.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可可娜酱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.82,0:09:40.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.98,0:09:42.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去看看纪念品吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.59,0:09:43.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.85,0:09:54.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下山也好累人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.97,0:09:56.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,满腿疮痍了都
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.47,0:10:01.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 不过烙印都集齐了 真好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.18,0:10:07.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵学姐之前想要这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.27,0:10:09.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那给她买一个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.51,0:10:13.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.66,0:10:15.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴士要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.49,0:10:19.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联系家里了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.08,0:10:21.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊对了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.65,0:10:26.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这电话其实不想打呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.74,0:10:28.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说了那么任性的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.42,0:10:30.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会生气的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.04,0:10:34.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.14,0:10:35.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.46,0:10:39.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 都没打电话 妈妈好担心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.55,0:10:41.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.36,0:10:43.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没坚持到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.81,0:10:46.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,声音没精打采的 没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.22,0:10:49.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 这就上巴士了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.12,0:10:53.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 忘记联络了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.58,0:10:56.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这么说 你尽力了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.85,0:11:00.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体没事吧 能坚持到家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.67,0:11:02.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.79,0:11:07.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 害妈妈操了这么多心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.61,0:11:09.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却还在鼓励我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.00,0:11:13.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪还有脸回家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.54,0:11:17.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.30,0:11:18.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵学姐
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wow, what's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.19,0:11:35.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好累
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.94,0:11:38.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头疼 腿也疼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.40,0:11:40.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好累
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.71,0:11:42.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再也不要这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.94,0:11:45.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,登山什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.82,0:11:59.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\pos(962,532)}待续
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(ED)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.08,0:12:04.49,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,Tinkling Smile 不思議と どうしてかな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.81,0:12:12.30,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,キミが笑うと 心の奥いつもキラリまたたく
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.52,0:12:14.94,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's little step! 一歩ずつ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.25,0:12:17.94,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's feel skip! 一緒にねっ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.19,0:12:30.59,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,気がつけば 夢中になってた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.83,0:12:35.96,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,「そういうコトあるよね」って言ってくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.21,0:12:41.76,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,キュッと手と手つないだら 伝わる ぬくもり
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.08,0:12:46.55,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,どこにでも行けちゃう気がしてる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.95,0:12:52.82,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,Tin-Ton-Tan 踏み出した瞬間に
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.99,0:12:58.38,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,世界がパノラマみたいにひらけたの
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.94,0:13:03.52,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,Tinkling Smile こんな空の広さ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.77,0:13:09.75,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,一人きりじゃ きっと気づけなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.96,0:13:14.62,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,Tinkling Smile 笑顔こだましてる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.81,0:13:22.40,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,胸に広がる やさしい うれしい あたらしい予感たち
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.06,0:13:27.88,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,一歩一歩進んで行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.08,0:12:04.49,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tinkling Smile 多么不可思议 是为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.81,0:12:12.30,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}看到你微笑 心中就像繁星般闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.52,0:12:14.94,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Let's little step! 一步一步
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.25,0:12:17.94,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Let's feel skip! 一起来呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.19,0:12:30.59,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}回过神来 已经沉浸其中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.83,0:12:35.96,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}是你对我说 「常有的事情！」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.21,0:12:41.76,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}顺着紧握的双手 传来你的体温
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.08,0:12:46.55,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}仿佛能走到天涯海角
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.95,0:12:52.82,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}叮 咚 铛 迈出一步的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.99,0:12:58.38,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}世界像全景照片一样展现在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.94,0:13:03.52,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tinkling Smile 如此广阔的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.77,0:13:09.75,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}只身一人 一定不会发现
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.96,0:13:14.62,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tinkling Smile 笑容在回响
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.81,0:13:22.40,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}充满内心的温柔和喜悦 还有新的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.06,0:13:27.88,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}一步一步往前走吧！
